actor User
boundary ProductDetailPage
control ContactController
participant ":ContactService" as ContactService
participant ":ContactModel" as ContactModel
database Database

User->ProductDetailPage: 1. Click "Contact to buy"
activate ProductDetailPage
activate User
ProductDetailPage->ProductDetailPage: 2. Open contact modal (name, phone, message, quantity)
activate ProductDetailPage
space
deactivate ProductDetailPage

User->ProductDetailPage: 3. Fill contact info and submit
ProductDetailPage->ProductDetailPage: 4. Validate input (required fields, phone format, quantity > 0)
activate ProductDetailPage
space
deactivate ProductDetailPage

opt Check validation
    ProductDetailPage-->User: 4.1. Show validation error
end

ProductDetailPage->ContactController: 5. POST /contacts/buy { productId, name, phone, message, quantity }
activate ContactController

ContactController->ContactService: 6. Process contact to buy request
activate ContactService

alt Product not found / unavailable
    ContactService->ContactModel: 7.1. Check product availability
    activate ContactModel

    ContactModel->Database: 7.1.1. Retrieve product status by ID
    activate Database
    Database-->ContactModel: 7.1.2. Result
    deactivate Database

    ContactModel-->ContactService: 7.1.3. Return invalid product state
    deactivate ContactModel

    ContactService-->ContactController: 7.1.4. Return error result
    ContactController-->ProductDetailPage: 7.1.5. Return 400/404 + message
    ProductDetailPage-->User: 7.1.6. Show error
else Product valid
    ContactService->ContactModel: 7.2. Create contact request record
    activate ContactModel

    ContactModel->Database: 7.2.1. Persist contact request
    activate Database
    Database-->ContactModel: 7.2.2. Created
    deactivate Database

    ContactModel-->ContactService: 7.2.3. Return created contact request
    deactivate ContactModel

    ContactService-->ContactController: 7.2.4. Return ContactToBuyResponse
    deactivate ContactService
    ContactController-->ProductDetailPage: 7.2.5. Return 200 OK + success message
    deactivate ContactController
    ProductDetailPage-->User: 7.2.6. Show success
end

deactivate ProductDetailPage
deactivate User
```